{"tid":1555642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你地咪當派膠，羅犯婦人係為左令人忽略新屋嶺輪姦事件先貶低女義士","createTime":"2019-09-09T12:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T13:08:07.000Z","uid":282006,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4a387bad2eb222075924b957bac2e241b53f939f","tid":1555642,"uid":282006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:04:08.000Z","msg":"同831太子站一樣，你對外文宣唔可以直接話有，不過可以用番同黑警一樣既方式令人spin向黑警犯罪：<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攞證據出黎！好人好姐收收埋埋做乜，律師家人都唔比入唔比見，身有屎呀！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為新屋嶺呢種地方，只有黑警喺度全權操控，或者黨鐵故意銷毀CCTV<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,fc責任根本不在一般人手中，叫天不應叫地不聞點fact check，你有無諗過呢d發生係女義士身上既慘劇可以造成幾大打擊，點樣公開講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句到尾，呢場抗爭未完之前，一概當有輪姦事件存在，831的確死左人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不過唔需要直接講有定無，大家只需要好似太子站獻花咁，用一個行動表現出呢種可能，只係黑警同政府否認而<span style=\"color: orange;\">沉冤未雪</span>就得</span><br />\n<br />\n呢一刻你掛住所謂FC只係反映根本無面對現實，自己面對緊一個道德無下限既對手，大家要保持憤怒，憤怒係抗爭既最原點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化，不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n將強姦犯殺人犯黑警一個不留地送落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4341aee1113d804d22fb10abaf27997801b67ae4","tid":1555642,"uid":282006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:06:22.000Z","msg":"p牌無得推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216e69f74d5dde1047265d627e59bb061a733af1","tid":1555642,"uid":55233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:08:08.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n太子同新屋嶺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一樣不能原諒 不能忘記"},{"pid":"5ad416a07817df80b7cddc5e4776800e5cd52353","tid":1555642,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e775c0e5baef3a27f7d603666cb4b35b7a6b96","tid":1555642,"uid":48868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff32d81af249d97db59f31c69e3980f655b54bdc","tid":1555642,"uid":38778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:25:43.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 831"},{"pid":"d4176bfcd8ff94d4872ba2ced4226b307aa61557","tid":1555642,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b30e01336bf60a02f7a83f673826099c72126db","tid":1555642,"uid":170297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:27:03.000Z","msg":"冷處理啦，唔好俾人帶風向。"},{"pid":"91e5a6a729f75453eb8dee55ffd8d16257846791","tid":1555642,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9420743eedc5fc03c07933a0286f546f8cc675ac","tid":1555642,"uid":48057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:25:34.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"76fd0bd4b94c24013ca9bf13146f5c6f1da80180","tid":1555642,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:26:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2d682cf4b985b0b2a940d766658b6500497c3fb3","tid":1555642,"uid":108462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:26:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e52a8b0d19e15ebc6fc7707366ab43614badf9b7","tid":1555642,"uid":102089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:29:59.000Z","msg":"此仇永世不忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5ca8e88abfab39179593bd5db766ffa193ac3d","tid":1555642,"uid":285195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"請唔好唔記得，擁有西方國家國籍既受害人(包括BNO)可以向西方國家領事館求助的！<br />\n<br />\nRape and sexual assault abroad: returning to the UK<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/rape-and-sexual-assault-abroad-returning-to-the-uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fpublications%2Frape-and-sexual-assault-abroad-returning-to-the-uk&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2ButOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=63905a72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/rape-and-sexual-assault-abroad-returning-to-the-uk</a><br />\n<br />\n當中一定有擁有西方國家國籍既受害人(包括BNO)，最起碼係一定要俾領事館職員black and white正式接收求助個案，因為即使以領事館既情報能力，佢哋係必定已經知道有咁既事發生，但無論如何佢哋係一定要接收過正式black and white既求助，先至可以正式介入協助，否則好難有足夠既介入理由。<br />\n<br />\n用呢個方法，領事館要做嘢未必一定需要受害人出面面對鏡頭面對公眾，但就應該係暫時嚟講比較能夠對港共黑警班人渣有效施壓既方法。所以有可能係最照顧到受害者感受而又能收比較上最大效果既方法。<br />\n<br />\n必需要記住，就算BNO都係正式英國國籍！即係話BNO都係英國僑民！自己國家既僑民喺外國蒙難，以西方國家嚟講係絕無可能咩都唔做的，只不過以依家時勢，西方國家有佢哋自己既agenda同time table，英國政府未出聲唔等於唔做嘢，所以幾時出手，用咩手段去處理求助，<br />\n要睇時機，呢個因素係我哋無法控制的。<br />\n<br />\n雖然技術上BNO到目前為止都仲係喺香港不受英國領事保護，不過BNO平權已經甚囂塵上，事成既話介時BNO都會獲發BC passport，再者當中英聯合聲明已經徹底被中國走數，英國隨時可以作相應行動，啟動對BNO提供領事保護。即係話冇人知邊時邊刻BNO突然可以同BC一樣享有英國領事保護。所以即使只係BNO都好，請務必唔理三七廿一先向領事館求助咗先再算，佢哋點都唔會好似班人渣黑警咁，喺以前太平盛世時都借故打發報案人走。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"b69ac3b1861b553d458bf49f260861a766841460","tid":1555642,"uid":311337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:08:07.000Z","msg":"推"}]}